data.description: Charming 4 bed, 1 bathroom home in the heart of West Scranton. Upon entering, you'll immediately notice the cozy and inviting atmosphere that permeates the entire space. The stain glass windows are just one feature that accentuate the true character of the home. This 3-story home offers Central AC, a finished 3rd floor that boasts a 4th bedroom with a walk-in closet & extra storage space. The fully-cover front porch and 3 season sunroom make relaxation effortless. A true gem that can only be fully appreciated in person!, Baths: 1 Bath Lev 2, Beds: 2+ Bed 2nd,1 Bed 3rd, SqFt Fin - Main: 805.00, SqFt Fin - 3rd: 240.00, Tax Information: Available, Formal Dining Room: Y, Modern Kitchen: Y, SqFt Fin - 2nd: 803.00
